– May wear helmets.
– May wear any armor and use any weapon.
– May get five stars in any weapon category.
– Gets one bonus feat at level 1 and at every even level.
– At 1st level gets Armor Training with leather and studded leather armor passive feat that allows to ignore armor skill and AC penalties. Gets Armor Training with hide armor and chainmails at level 4, splint mails at level 8, plate mails at level 12 and finally full plate mails at level 16.
– Hit Die: d10 
