	@011=~BARBARIAN: A Barbarian can be an excellent warrior. While not as disciplined or as skilled as a Fighter, the Barbarian can willingly throw <PRO_HIMHER>self into a berserker rage, becoming a tougher and stronger opponent.

CLASS FEATURES:

– May not wear armor heavier than splint mail.
– May only get 1 star with any weapon class.
– Moves 2 points faster than other characters.
– Immune to sneak attack.
– Gets one bonus feat at level 5 and every 5 levels thereafter.
