	@501=~Barkskin 
(Alteration)

Level: 2
Sphere: Protection, Plant 
Range: Touch 
Duration: 4 rounds + 1 round/level 
Casting Time: 5 
Area of Effect: 1 creature 
Saving Throw: None 

When a priest casts the Barkskin spell upon a creature, its skin becomes as tough as bark, giving it +3 bonus to AC, bonus increases to +4 at 7th level and to +5 at 13th level. In addition, Saving Throws vs. all attack forms except magic gain a +1 bonus. This spell can be placed on the caster or on any other creature <PRO_HESHE> touches.~

	@502=~Shield
(Evocation)

Level: 1
Range: 0
Duration: 1 hour
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None

When this spell is cast, an invisible barrier comes into being in front of the wizard. It gives the wizard +4 bonus to AC. It also grants the wizard immunity from the spell Magic Missile. An AC bonus is lost if caster equips a shield. The effect lasts for the duration of the spell or until dispelled.~

	@503=~Champion's Strength
(Alteration)

Level: 5 
Sphere: Law
Range: 0
Duration: 3 rounds/level
Casting Time: 2
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None 

When this spells is cast, the priest effectively draws on the strength of <PRO_HISHER> god through himself becoming an ultimate fighting machine. Caster's base THAC0 becomes equal to that of a fighter of the same level and <PRO_HESHE> receive +1/2 additional attack per round. Also <PRO_HESHE> gets a +4 Strength bonus for the duration of the spell and receives all the bonuses to hit and damage rolls that this Strength confers.

The drawback to this is that the priest must concentrate on the connection with <PRO_HISHER> god for the duration of the spell, hence losing the ability to cast any spells during this time. The effect lasts for 3 rounds for every level of the caster or until dispelled.~
//--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------//
	@5031=~Holy Power
(Evocation)

Level: 4
Range: 0
Duration: 1 round/level
Casting Time: 6
Area of Effect: The caster
Saving Throw: None

Through this spell, the caster imbues <PRO_HIMHER>self with the strength and skill of a Fighter of the same level. The priest's Strength score is increased by 2 —<PRO_HISHER> THAC0 becomes that of a Fighter of the same level, <PRO_HISHER> number of attacks per round increases by 1/2, and <PRO_HESHE> gains 1 temporary Hit Point per level. This will last for the duration of the spell or until dispelled. Priest looses the ability to cast spells while under the effect of Holy Power.~
